==历史==

===十九世纪===
[[File:Corporal_Joseph_Pierce.jpg|right]][[下士|下士]]，第一位有影像资料可考的华裔美国军人]]
早在[[美国独立战争|独立战争]]期间就有菲律宾裔美国海兵服役的传闻轶事<ref name="GN" />。然而，官方文件记载中第一次出现亚裔士兵是在1815年第二次独立战争期间<ref name="AFPS" />，后来担任第七任美国总统的[[安德鲁·杰克逊|安德鲁·杰克逊]][[少将|少将]]记录自己的部属{{Link-en|吉恩·拉菲特|Jean Lafitte}}的麾下有“马尼拉人（Manilamen）”参与了[[新奥尔良战役|新奥尔良之战]]<ref name="AFPS" />。战争结束后，至少有一位叫做奥古斯汀·菲利奇亚诺（Augustin Feliciano）的菲裔军人继续在美国海军服役<ref>{{cite book |title=Filipinos of Greater Philadelphia |last=Silva |first=Eliseo Art Arambulo |last2=Peralt |first2=Victorina Alvarez |year=2012 |publisher=Arcadia Publishing |isbn=9780738592695 |page=9 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=WsDpsSeBO3kC&lpg=PA9&ots=xg2o22yrNm&dq=%22The%20Largest%20Colony%20of%20Filipinos%20in%20America%22&pg=PA9#v=onepage&q=%22The%20Largest%20Colony%20of%20Filipinos%20in%20America%22&f=false |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627191953/http://books.google.com/books?id=WsDpsSeBO3kC&lpg=PA9&ots=xg2o22yrNm&dq=%22The%20Largest%20Colony%20of%20Filipinos%20in%20America%22&pg=PA9#v=onepage&q=%22The%20Largest%20Colony%20of%20Filipinos%20in%20America%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之后，亚裔美国人再度出现在{{Link-en|美国军事史|Military history of the United States}}是在1861年——南北战争期间，一位名叫约翰·汤姆尼（John Tomney）的华裔美国人在联邦军的纽约州步兵团服役<ref name="CHCP">{{cite web |last=Williams |first=Rudi |title=Asian/Pacific American Military Timeline |url=http://chcp.org/virtual-museum-library/asianpacific-american-military-timeline/ |year=1999 |work=Memorial Day, 1999 |publisher=Defense Equal Opportunity Management Institute |accessdate=2009-08-26 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222095614/http://chcp.org/virtual-museum-library/asianpacific-american-military-timeline/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他在[[葛底斯堡战役|葛底斯堡战役]]伤重阵亡<ref name="APAT">{{cite news |first=Rudi |last=Williams |title=An Asian Pacific American Timeline |url=http://www.ntac.hawaii.edu/AAPIcourse/downloads/doc/AsianPacificAmerican_timeline.doc |work=American Forces Press Service |publisher=U.S. Department of Defense |date=1999-05-19 |accessdate=2009-08-27 |quote=21-1861 Chinese American John Tomney joins New York Infantry, later dies of wounds at Battle of Gettysburg (1863). |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090918011523/http://www.ntac.hawaii.edu/AAPIcourse/downloads/doc/AsianPacificAmerican_timeline.doc |archivedate=2009-09-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=China at Gettysburg |author= |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1863/07/12/news/china-at-gettysburg.html?scp=23&sq=Gettysburg&st=p |newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=1863-07-12 |accessdate=2012-07-05 |quote=Among the killed at Gettysburgh was a young; Chinaman, known as JOHN TOMMY. |archive-date=2013-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618185258/http://www.nytimes.com/1863/07/12/news/china-at-gettysburg.html?scp=23&sq=Gettysburg&st=p |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

还有一位更名为[[约瑟夫·皮尔斯|约瑟夫·皮尔斯]]的华裔美国人，一般认为他由身为康涅狄格号船长的养父阿莫斯·派克（Amos Peck）由中国带来<ref name="JosephPierce">{{cite web|url=http://www.gdg.org/Research/People/jpierce.html|title=Joseph Pierce|author=|date=|work=Gettysburg Discussion Group|publisher=|accessdate=2011-01-16|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717054304/http://www.gdg.org/Research/People/jpierce.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。皮尔斯于1862年7月26日从军，分配到第14康涅狄格州步兵团F连，隶属于[[波多马克军团|波多马克军团]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:6Iz52T8doFUJ:https://www.nps.gov/fopu/planyourvisit/upload/asian-site-bulletin-final.pdf+&cd=1&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=us |title=Soldiers Biographies |author= |date= |work=Gettysburg National Military Park |publisher=National Park Service |accessdate=2011-01-16}}</ref>。从1862年到1865年，皮尔斯参与了{{Link-en|安提耶坦之战|Battle of Antietam}}、葛底斯堡之战直到最后[[罗伯特·李|李将军]]{{Link-en|阿波马托克斯法院之战|Battle of Appomattox Court House|投降于阿波马托克斯法院}}的所有关键性战役<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.army.mil/asianpacificsoldiers/history/civilwar.html|title=Civil War|author=|date=|work=|publisher=United States Army|accessdate=2011-01-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110624063104/http://www.army.mil/asianpacificsoldiers/history/civilwar.html|archivedate=2011-06-24}}</ref>。皮尔斯在战争中升任[[下士|下士]]，是为当时联邦军所有华裔美国人中军衔最高者<ref>{{cite book |title=Encyclopedia of the American Civil War: a political, social, and military history |last=Stephen Heidler |first=David |coauthors=Jeanne T. Heidler, David J. Coles |year=2002 |publisher=W. W. Norton & Company |isbn=978-0-393-04758-5 |page=434 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=SdrYv7S60fgC&pg=PA434&lpg=PA434&dq=Corporal+Joseph+Pierce+chinese&source=bl&ots=lX0CyOQyHC&sig=8ReYYt6MEl64HDECB6WLcho4Uak&hl=en&ei=CoozTcHRGorCsAPn5ozWBQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CEsQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=Corporal%20Joseph%20Pierce%20chinese&f=false |accessdate=2011-01-16}}</ref>，他的照片成為葛底斯堡博物馆館藏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gdg.org/Research/People/jpierce.html |title=Joseph Pierce, |author= |date= |work= |publisher= |accessdate=2011-01-16 |archive-date=2011-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717054304/http://www.gdg.org/Research/People/jpierce.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年，[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]通过一项决议，表彰了皮尔斯和其他亚太裔军人在南北战争中的表现<ref>{{cite web |title=H. Res. 415 [110th]: Honoring Edward Day Cohota, Joseph L. Pierce, and other veterans of Asian and Pacific Islander... (GovTrack.us) |url=http://www.govtrack.us/congress/bill.xpd?bill=hr110-415 |work=Honoring Edward Day Cohota, Joseph L. Pierce, and other veterans of Asian and Pacific Islander descent who fought in the U.S. Civil War. |publisher=110th Congress 2007–2008 |accessdate=2011-05-30}}</ref>。

威廉·韩亚（William Ah Hang）则成为了第一位在美国海军服役的华裔，他于1863年从军<ref name="CHCP"/>。据统计，在南北战争期间，总共有不少于50名华裔军人分别效命于联邦军和邦联军<ref name="AFPS"/>。在他们之中，只有少数人取得了抚恤金、福利和入籍等待遇。其中有位叫做李清（Ching Lee），别名为托马斯·西尔瓦努斯（Thomas Sylvanus）的人是个例外，他曾在第81宾夕法尼亚州步兵团服役（81st Pennsylvania Regiment）<ref>{{cite web |last=Lin |first=Sam Chu |title=Chinese American Civil War Veteran Honored In Pennsylvania Ceremonies |url=http://www.committee100.org/media/media_eng/sam_chu_lin.html |work=Articles of Interest |publisher=Committee of 100, inc. |accessdate=2009-08-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205073257/http://www.committee100.org/media/media_eng/sam_chu_lin.html |archivedate=2010-02-05 |df= }}</ref>。

南北战争期间，路易斯安那有许多菲裔加入邦联军<ref name="GN">{{cite web |url=http://www.inquirer.net/globalnation/col_gln/2005/oct03.htm |title=Filipinos in Louisiana |author=Rodel E. Rodis |work=Global Nation |publisher=www.inq7.net |accessdate=2011-02-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090906083110/http://www.inquirer.net/globalnation/col_gln/2005/oct03.htm |archivedate=2009-09-06 }}</ref>，其中有一位服役于[[阿拉巴马号战列舰_(美利坚联盟国)|阿拉巴马号战列舰]]<ref>{{cite book |title=Filipinos and Their Revolution: Event, Discourse, and Historiography |last=Ileto |first=Reynaldo Clemeña |year=1998 |publisher=Ateneo University Press |isbn=9789715502948 |page=121 |accessdate=2012-08-20 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=u92ZR42UhpIC&lpg=PA121&ots=oO_CMhG87D&dq=Filipino%20Confederates&pg=PA121#v=onepage&q=Filipino%20Confederates&f=false |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627192213/http://books.google.com/books?id=u92ZR42UhpIC&lpg=PA121&ots=oO_CMhG87D&dq=Filipino%20Confederates&pg=PA121#v=onepage&q=Filipino%20Confederates&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还有一部分人成为了路易斯安那义勇军<ref>{{cite book |title=Hispanic Confederates |last=O'Donnell-Rosales |first=John |year=2006 |publisher=Genealogical Publishing Com |location=[[Baltimore|Baltimore]] |isbn=978-0-8063-5230-5 |page=ix |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Jsuy2CLtuD0C&lpg=PR9&ots=EmtaY__lLC&dq=Confederacy%20Filipino%20Americans%20Louisiana&pg=PR9#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=2011-02-15 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629124054/http://books.google.com/books?id=Jsuy2CLtuD0C&lpg=PR9&ots=EmtaY__lLC&dq=Confederacy%20Filipino%20Americans%20Louisiana&pg=PR9#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在北方，一名叫做菲利克斯·鲍德利（Felix Cornelius Balderry）的菲裔则加入了联邦军{{Link-en|第11密歇根志愿步兵团|11th Michigan Volunteer Infantry Regiment}}<ref>{{cite news |title=Filipinos display proud heritage exhibit at Five Corners Library |author=Brett Wishe |url=http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2010/11/filipinos_display_proud_herita.html |newspaper=The Jersey Journal |date=2010-11-02 |accessdate=2011-05-19 |quote=Filled with photos and mini-essays, including old newspaper documents, it chronicles the roles of influential Filipino-Americans, from San Francisco Giants pitcher Tim Lincecum to Felix Cornelius Balderry, a Union soldier in the Civil War. |archive-date=2010-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213190854/http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2010/11/filipinos_display_proud_herita.html |dead-url=no }}<br/>{{cite book |title=Michigan and the Civil War: A Great and Bloody Sacrifice |last=Dempsey |first=Jack |year=2011 |publisher=The History Press |location=Charleston, SC |isbn=978-1-60949-173-4 |page=88 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=on6b2Pcl1lIC&lpg=PA88&ots=QVjBoYsdR3&dq=Felix%20Balderry%20civil%20war%20michigan&pg=PA88#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=2011-05-19 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627191813/http://books.google.com/books?id=on6b2Pcl1lIC&lpg=PA88&ots=QVjBoYsdR3&dq=Felix%20Balderry%20civil%20war%20michigan&pg=PA88#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在南北战争末期直至[[美西战争|美西战争]]这段时间鲜有亚裔服役之记录，直到[[緬因號戰艦_(ACR-1)|缅因号战列舰]]沉没于[[古巴|古巴]][[哈瓦那|哈瓦那湾]]，伤亡报告显示有7名日裔和1名华裔<ref name="DEOMI" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.public.navy.mil/bupers-npc/reference/messages/Documents2/NAVADMINS2/NAV2007/NAV07091.txt |title=RAAUZYUW RUENAAA7101 1082000-UUUU—RUCRNAD |author=VADM J.C. Harvey Jr. |date=2007-04-18 |work= |publisher=United States Navy |accessdate=2011-05-29 |quote=Seven first-generation Japanese Americans and one Chinese American where killed when the U.S.S. Main was sunk in Havana Harbor in 1898. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222033438/https://www.public.navy.mil/bupers-npc/reference/messages/Documents2/NAVADMINS2/NAV2007/NAV07091.txt |archive-date=2019-02-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在随后的美菲战争中，有7名日裔海兵在美国战舰上服役，并参与了[[馬尼拉灣|马尼拉湾]]海战<ref name="APAT"/>。

