0120618235749/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/global-filipino/06/18/12/pinoy-sailors-us-navy-eye-deployment-ph |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{As of|2013|01|24}}，在新世纪的[[反恐战争|反恐战争]]中阵亡的2165位军人中，有58人是亚裔（44名来自陆军、8名来自海军陆战队和6名来自海军）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dmdc.osd.mil/dcas/pages/report_oef_deaths.xhtml |title=U.S. Military Casualties – Operation Enduring Freedom (OEF) Military Deaths |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2013-01-24 |work=Defense Manpower Data Center |publisher=United States Department of Defense |accessdate=2013-01-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221224440/https://www.dmdc.osd.mil/dcas/pages/report_oef_deaths.xhtml |archivedate=2013-02-21 }}</ref> ，另有352亚裔军人负伤（274名来自陆军、56名来自海军陆战队、17名来自海军、5名来自空军）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dmdc.osd.mil/dcas/pages/report_oef_wounded.xhtml |title=U.S. Military Casualties – Operation Enduring Freedom (OEF) Wounded in Action |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2013-01-24 |work=Defense Manpower Data Center |publisher=United States Department of Defense |accessdate=2013-01-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221224501/https://www.dmdc.osd.mil/dcas/pages/report_oef_wounded.xhtml |archivedate=2013-02-21 }}</ref>。

