And Honors Information: 100th Battalion, 442nd Infantry Regiment |author= |date=2011-01-14 |work=U.S. Army Center of Military History |publisher=United States Army |accessdate=2011-03-14 |archive-date=2011-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110312075639/http://www.history.army.mil/html/forcestruc/lineages/branches/inf/0442in100bn.htm |dead-url=no }}<br/>{{cite news |title= 100th Battalion marks Yule in Iraq |author= Gregg K. Kakesako |url= http://archives.starbulletin.com/2005/12/25/news/story09.html |newspaper= Honolulu Star-Bulletin |date= 2005-12-25 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100808230008/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2005/12/25/news/story09.html |archivedate= 2010-08-08 |accessdate= 2011-03-14 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。在派驻期结束时，部队獲准使用第442步兵团的标志，这也是该单位袖章自二战后首次投入使用<ref>{{cite news |title=Some Hawai'i citizen-soldiers must trade-in patches earned in combat |author=William Cole |url=http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Mar/21/ln/FP603210349.html |newspaper=Honolulu Advertiser |date=2006-03-21 |accessdate=2013-02-07 |archive-date=2012-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022051803/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Mar/21/ln/FP603210349.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。2008年至2009年期间，第100步兵营再度转為现役部隊派驻伊拉克<ref>{{cite news |title=Gold medal honors, inspires |url=http://www.staradvertiser.com/editorials/20101007_Gold_medal_honors_inspires.html |newspaper=Honolulu Star Advertiser |date=2010-10-07 |accessdate=2011-03-14 |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112123631/http://www.staradvertiser.com/editorials/20101007_Gold_medal_honors_inspires.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在新一轮的行动中，有82名亚裔军人阵亡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fas.org/sgp/crs/natsec/RS22452.pdf |title=U.S. Military Casualty Statistics: Operation New Dawn, Operation Iraqi Freedom, and Operation Enduring Freedom |author=Hannah Fischer |date=2010-09-28 |work= |publisher=Congressional Research Service |accessdate=2011-03-14 |