==领导人物==
第一位晉陞将官的亚裔美国人是母系拥有部分华人血统的莱曼准将（Brigadier General Albert Lyman）<ref>{{cite news |title=Lyman Brothers, First Asian Americans to Gain General’s Rank |author=Lisa Wong Macabasco |url=http://www.asianweek.com/2008/01/22/lyman-brothers-first-asian-americans-to-gain-general%E2%80%99s-rank/ |newspaper=Asian Week |date=2008-01-22 |accessdate=2011-05-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604192312/http://www.asianweek.com/2008/01/22/lyman-brothers-first-asian-americans-to-gain-general%E2%80%99s-rank/ |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref>。在他之后的[[钟云|钟云]]少将成为了美国海军第一位亚裔将官<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.history.navy.mil/content/dam/nhhc/browse-by-topic/diversity/Asians%20and%20Pacific%20Islanders%20in%20the%20Navy/pdf/API-12Apr11.pdf |title=Asians Asians and Pacific Islanders and in the United States Navy |author= |date=2011-04-12 |work=Naval History & Heritage Command |publisher=United States Navy |accessdate=2011-05-01 |quote=Gordon Chung-Hoon, a Hawaiian-born Chinese American and a 1934 U.S. Naval Academy graduate, was the first Asian American to command a Navy warship, USS ''Sigsbee'' (dd 502). When a kamikaze attacked caused explosions and flooding on board the destroyer, Chung-Hoon directed damage control, enabling the crew to save the ship. Awarded the Navy Cross for his actions, he was later promoted to rear admiral, making him the first Asian American flag officer. |archive-date=2015-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205070255/http://www.history.navy.mil/content/dam/nhhc/browse-by-topic/diversity/Asians%20and%20Pacific%20Islanders%20in%20the%20Navy/pdf/API-12Apr11.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> <!--As of Fall 2012, there have been 43 Japanese American, 26 Chinese Americans, 10 Filipino American, and four Korean American general and flag officers in the [[Uniformed_services_of_the_United_States|Uniformed services of the United States]].<ref>{{cite journal |year=2012 |title=Meet the Generals and Admirals |journal=JAVA Advocate |volume=XX |issue=3 |pages=10 |publisher=Japanese American Veterans Association |url=http://javadc.org/media/document/java-advocate/JAVA-Advocate-Fall-2012.pdf |accessdate=2013-01-21 }}</ref>-->。亚裔军人所获军衔中等级最高者是第34任美国陆军参谋长[[艾力·新关|艾力·新关]]将军，他与[[哈里·B·哈里斯|哈里·B·哈里斯]]为目前仅有的美軍亚裔四星上将<ref>{{cite news |title=Obama accepts resignation of VA Secretary Shinseki |author=Greg Jaffe and Ed O'Keefe |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/shinseki-apologizes-for-va-health-care-scandal/2014/05/30/e605885a-e7f0-11e3-8f90-73e071f3d637_story.html?utm_term=.d2e0ae4e95e4 |newspaper=Washington Post |date=2014-05-30 |accessdate=2017-06-27 |quote= |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513111625/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/shinseki-apologizes-for-va-health-care-scandal/2014/05/30/e605885a-e7f0-11e3-8f90-73e071f3d637_story.html?utm_term=.d2e0ae4e95e4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

近年来，亚裔美国军校学员在联邦级别军事院校中的比例已显著超出亚裔在美国所占人口比例。尽管18到24岁之间的亚太裔美国人只占这个年龄段总人口的3.49%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RkF3cGkv5R8C&pg=PA173&lpg=PA173&dq=Racial+Composition+of+New+Enlisted+Recruits+in+2006+and+2007.+The+Heritage+Foundation&source=bl&ots=-MNBMxKBhB&sig=QQA1J4mSQCxKMK1m6D6FzAb2Otg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiDlIqCld_UAhVI3IMKHchsD7MQ6AEINTAC#v=onepage&q=Racial%20Composition%20of%20New%20Enlisted%20Recruits%20in%202006%20and%202007.%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation&f=false |title=Racial Composition of New Enlisted Recruits in 2006 and 2007 |author= |year=2008 |work= |publisher=The Heritage Foundation |accessdate=2011-06-11 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513172934/https://books.google.com/books?id=RkF3cGkv5R8C&pg=PA173&lpg=PA173&dq=Racial+Composition+of+New+Enlisted+Recruits+in+2006+and+2007.+The+Heritage+Foundation&source=bl&ots=-MNBMxKBhB&sig=QQA1J4mSQCxKMK1m6D6FzAb2Otg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiDlIqCld_UAhVI3IMKHchsD7MQ6AEINTAC#v=onepage&q=Racial%20Composition%20of%20New%20Enlisted%20Recruits%20in%202006%20and%202007.%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他们在西点军校、[[美国海军学院|海军学院]]和[[美国空军学院|空军学院]]2014届的学员中所占比例达10%左右<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.westpoint.edu/Dcomm/PressReleasesbd/nr41-10class_of_2014_RDay.html |title=News Release |author=Public Affairs Office |date=2010-06-21 |work= |publisher=United States Military Academy |accessdate=2011-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722114548/http://www.westpoint.edu/Dcomm/PressReleasesbd/nr41-10class_of_2014_RDay.html |archive-date=2011-07-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usna.edu/PAO/documents/PlebeProfile_Class_of_2018.pdf |title=2018 Class Portrait |author= |date= |work= |publisher=United States Naval Academy |accessdate=2017-06-27 |archive-date=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708131801/https://www.usna.edu/PAO/documents/PlebeProfile_Class_of_2018.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>